This paper focuses on reinforcement learning and policy generalization, which are core topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also mentions data augmentation, meta-learning, and adversarial training, which are common techniques used in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential of these techniques for system control (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, and cs.SY.
